For starters yu will need to download mysql 
1. look up mysql on the browser 
2.click on downloads, then inside downloads click on community downloads
3. Here you will need to select the installer for windows
4. Go through the installation menus by clicking next until you get to the password 
5. Create a password that is easy to remember 
6. Click next and it will start to download the different connections
7. Make sure to use the same password to secure you connection
8. When your root is ready to be used you can open an mysql script from the self contained file in the github
